{"type":"message","id":"6d644a5f","parentId":"132cb175","timestamp":"2026-02-27T03:12:55.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🤡 行，那我先建个 `memory/RECENT.md`，把刚才的对话要点记进去。以后每次对话结束我都更新它。\n\n另外，我刚才翻了下记忆目录，发现文件挺乱的——有 `2025-01-16.md`、`2026-02-13.md`，还有今天的 `2026-02-27.md`。以后我定期整理，把过期的 daily notes 归档或者删掉。\n\n现在 RECENT.md 已经建好了，下次你 `/new` 的时候记得提醒我读它，或者你自己加到启动流程里。\n\n还有别的事不？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":12516,"output":123,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12639,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772161971273}}
