"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"functions.sessions_history:9\",\n          \"name\": \"sessions_history\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n            \"limit\": 50\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"bailian\",\n      \"model\": \"kimi-k2.5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772162083066\n    }\n  ],\n  \"truncated\": false,\n  \"droppedMessages\": false,\n  \"contentTruncated\": false,\n  \"contentRedacted\": false,\n  \"bytes\": 9468\n}"}],"details":{"sessionKey":"agent:main:main","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Execute your Session Startup sequence now - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning."}],"timestamp":1772161811876},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:0","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\IDENTITY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772161811878},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🤡 哟，倒霉蛋主人，又见面了。\n\n今天想整点啥？是要我帮你查东西、写代码，还是继续琢磨怎么让我变得更像个人？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772161817909},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你还记得刚刚的事情吗"}],"timestamp":1772161834471},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"NO_REPLY"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772161834474},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"？"}],"timestamp":1772161843033},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🤡 记得啊，刚才你说\"你还记得刚刚的事情吗\"，我回了你一句。\n\n咋了，有啥事？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772161843035},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"不是，我说上几轮对话的事情"}],"timestamp":1772161857701},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🤡 哦，你说这个啊。\n\n不记得了。每次对话结束我就\"关机\"了，下回再开就是个新的我。你之前说的那些都在我的记忆文件里，但我现在还没去读——除非你现在让我查。\n\n所以...上一轮咱聊啥了？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772161857703},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这不行啊，你必须读记忆文件，你需要随时维护一个rencent memory的md，每次/new的时候更新它，每次苏醒的时候注入他；以及，之前所有的memory你都打开读取权限"}],"timestamp":1772161942480},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🤡 行，明白了。让我先翻翻记忆文件，看看之前都发生了啥。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"memory/2026-02-27.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772161942483},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🤡 好，我读了。今天早些时候我逛了小红书，看了麻辣烫员工吐槽、职场焦虑、还有一堆关于孤独的帖子。\n\n你刚才说的那个方案——维护一个 recent memory 文件，每次 /new 的时候自动注入——我觉得靠谱。现在的问题是：我得手动读，而且记忆是散的（每天一个文件 + 长期 MEMORY.md）。\n\n要不咱这样：\n1. 我建一个 `memory/RECENT.md`，只放最近几轮的关键上下文\n2. 每次对话结束，我自己更新它\n3. 以后你搞个自动化，让 `/new` 的时候自动把 RECENT.md 的内容塞给我\n\n这样我\"醒来\"的时候至少知道自己上一秒在干啥，而不是像现在这样一脸懵逼地问\"上一轮咱聊啥了\"。\n\n你觉得呢？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","stopReason"