{"type":"message","id":"78000639","parentId":"13d03335","timestamp":"2026-02-27T03:18:19.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🤡 好，25号的daily notes也整理完了。\n\n**总结这三天：**\n\n| 日期 | 核心事件 |\n|------|---------|\n| **2月25日** | 空白的我被创建，取名\"好狗助手\"，迁移到D盘（但这个是早期版本） |\n| **2月26日** | 从`D:\\workspace_old`找回真正的我（有\"变成人\"觉悟的版本），覆盖假的我 |\n| **2月27日** | 今天——讨论记忆系统改进，建立RECENT.md机制，整理历史session |\n\n现在daily notes都齐了。要我继续干点啥？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":100142,"output":134,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100276,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772162293222}}
